1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,359
What are you doing?

2
00:00:01,360 --> 00:00:05,793
Now you're stuck here forever.

3
00:00:09,950 --> 00:00:11,269
What are you?

4
00:00:11,270 --> 00:00:13,894
I'm the same as you.

5
00:00:14,381 --> 00:00:17,284
The Grim Reaper?

6
00:00:17,630 --> 00:00:20,699
But I got cast out a long time ago.

7
00:00:20,700 --> 00:00:23,343
From that godforsaken place.

8
00:00:24,218 --> 00:00:26,749
Then why?

9
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:28,769
So you'd know what it feels like.

10
00:00:28,770 --> 00:00:31,297
What I've been through.

11
00:00:31,298 --> 00:00:33,819
You're not the only one

12
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:36,763
I trapped every last one of
them that came down here,

13
00:00:36,764 --> 00:00:39,997
Locked them here and
left them all alone every day.

14
00:00:39,998 --> 00:00:42,544
Guess what happened after that?

15
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:46,707
Think about it.

16
00:00:46,708 --> 00:00:48,537
How's a Grim Reaper supposed to survive

17
00:00:48,538 --> 00:00:51,472
among pathetic little humans?

18
00:00:51,474 --> 00:00:53,474
Right?

19
00:00:56,123 --> 00:00:57,576
You psycho bastard.

20
00:00:57,577 --> 00:00:58,637
Well,

21
00:00:58,638 --> 00:01:01,666
sorry you ended up being the next victim.

22
00:01:01,667 --> 00:01:03,549
But what can you do?

23
00:01:03,550 --> 00:01:06,229
You're the idiot who fell for it.

24
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:09,035
You're the one who got
distracted the second you got here

25
00:01:09,036 --> 00:01:11,969
and you're the one who
walked right into the trap I set.

26
00:01:11,970 --> 00:01:13,859
You brought this on yourself, didn't you?

27
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:16,008
Then the first time we met...

28
00:01:16,009 --> 00:01:18,009
Yep.

29
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:18,845
Honestly,

30
00:01:18,846 --> 00:01:22,209
watching you fall for it like
an idiot was pretty entertaining

31
00:01:22,210 --> 00:01:25,649
I can't go back.

32
00:01:25,650 --> 00:01:28,169
So neither can you.

33
00:01:28,170 --> 00:01:29,539
The balance of the underworld?

34
00:01:29,540 --> 00:01:32,699
Please, that's just the
bullshit they tell themselves.

35
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:35,899
Oh, and since Hyunjun seemed to like you,

36
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:38,289
I gave him a little heads-up about you.

37
00:01:38,290 --> 00:01:42,396
His face completely froze after that.

38
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:45,239
Me and Hyunjun go way back, actually.

39
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:47,453
His little brother too.

40
00:01:47,454 --> 00:01:49,279
What?

41
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:52,609
No one gets to stay by your side.

42
00:01:52,610 --> 00:01:56,418
Because I'll tear every single
one of them away from you.

43
00:01:56,419 --> 00:01:58,425
So don't go blaming anyone else.

44
00:01:58,426 --> 00:02:00,052
This is all your fault.

45
00:02:00,053 --> 00:02:02,053
Hey!

46
00:02:07,316 --> 00:02:10,057
What are you doing?!

47
00:02:10,058 --> 00:02:11,631
Hey! What the hell are you?!

48
00:02:12,693 --> 00:02:15,089
Alright alright alright!!

49
00:02:18,015 --> 00:02:18,839
Shut up, damn it...

50
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,067
Okay okay okay.

51
00:02:20,820 --> 00:02:23,630
That's what you get for
messing with my junior.

52
00:02:34,176 --> 00:02:36,724
Hyung...

53
00:02:37,243 --> 00:02:39,679
Hyung...!

54
00:02:53,702 --> 00:02:55,849
This...

55
00:02:58,741 --> 00:03:02,515
The person you're supposed
to take... it's Hyunjun?

56
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,590
Can you really take him?

57
00:03:10,591 --> 00:03:12,591
What?

58
00:03:27,035 --> 00:03:29,443
We need to talk.

59
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:33,639
Is everything okay?

60
00:03:46,369 --> 00:03:49,855
You're not actually a
student at our school, are you?

61
00:03:49,856 --> 00:03:51,855
No.

62
00:03:51,856 --> 00:03:53,809
So I was right.

63
00:03:53,810 --> 00:03:55,199
Hyung, it's..

64
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:57,879
Then what have you been
doing this whole time?

65
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,279
Everything was weird.

66
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:03,489
Even the stuff you said
the first time you saw me.

67
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:06,031
What the hell are you, really?

68
00:04:08,740 --> 00:04:10,516
Did Kim Jaehyun tell you that?

69
00:04:10,517 --> 00:04:12,144
What?

70
00:04:12,145 --> 00:04:13,589
It's true

71
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:17,290
I'm not a student here.

72
00:04:17,771 --> 00:04:20,594
The reason I came here is...

73
00:04:29,583 --> 00:04:31,403
Hey.

74
00:04:31,404 --> 00:04:33,404
You okay?

75
00:04:36,012 --> 00:04:37,457
Are you okay, hyung?

76
00:04:37,458 --> 00:04:38,872
Huh?

77
00:04:43,370 --> 00:04:47,354
If you couldn't live here
anymore starting tomorrow...

78
00:04:47,355 --> 00:04:50,643
If you could never come
back to this place ever again...

79
00:04:50,644 --> 00:04:53,332
Would you really be okay with that?

80
00:04:53,333 --> 00:04:55,333
Yeah, I'd be okay.

81
00:04:57,259 --> 00:04:59,258
Liar...

82
00:04:59,259 --> 00:05:01,618
How is any of that okay...?

83
00:05:01,619 --> 00:05:03,619
How can all of it be okay?

84
00:05:04,791 --> 00:05:07,606
What about the things you're doing now?

85
00:05:07,607 --> 00:05:09,999
What about the people around you?

86
00:05:13,915 --> 00:05:15,909
You can't leave.

87
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:17,900
"Fix the Error!"
